      Line Width: 0.09000000357627869
      Name: Trajectory A*
      Offset:
        X: 0
        Y: 0
        Z: 0
      Pose Color: 255; 85; 255
      Pose Style: None
      Queue Size: 10
      Radius: 0.029999999329447746
      Shaft Diameter: 0.10000000149011612
      Shaft Length: 0.10000000149011612
      Topic: /esv_planner/trajectory_astar
